01:13.819 --> 01:15.044
THAT.

01:15.400 --> 01:17.101
WAY TO GO, BRAD!

01:21.001 --> 01:22.234
IS THAT HIS GIRLFRIEND?

01:22.301 --> 01:23.801
YEAH, HER NAME'S
KRISTA.

01:33.189 --> 01:34.292
I DON'T KNOW.

01:34.327 --> 01:36.975
WHAT HAPPENED?
NED, WHAT'S WRONG?

01:37.010 --> 01:38.317
BRAD'S POINTS AREN'T UP.

01:38.352 --> 01:40.273
SOMETHING WRONG
WITH THE SCOREBOARD.

01:40.308 --> 01:42.012
MAYBE SHE NEEDS HELP.

01:46.800 --> 01:53.094
"34 + GF = DEATH."

01:53.129 --> 01:53.995
WHAT'S GOING ON?

01:54.379 --> 01:55.869
34, THAT'S BRAD'S
NUMBER.

01:55.904 --> 01:57.807
SO "GF" IS GOTTA BE
GIRLFRIEND, RIGHT?

01:57.842 --> 02:01.266
YEAH, BRAD AND KRISTA
ARE LIKE THIS
UBER COUPLE.

02:01.301 --> 02:02.834
WHAT?

